                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9274" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0301</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">868 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“金花”开出金产业，乡村“链”出新责任：品品好粮油集团社会责任之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Golden flowers out of gold industry, rural chain new responsibility: the social responsibility road of Pinpinhao grain and oils group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">梁冰倩，卞亦文，霍伟伟，李海佳，金玲羽，倪子涵</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海大学MBA教育管理中心</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛品品好粮油集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">乡村振兴战略；企业社会责任；企业数字化转型；品牌营销与社会价值；电商直播营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Rural Revitalization Strategy, Corporate Social Responsibility, Enterprise Digital Transformation, Brand Marketing and Social Value, E-commerce Live Streaming Marketing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">    青岛品品好粮油集团自1996年创立以来，以数智技术创新为动力，致力于实现经济发展与社会责任的和谐共生。集团通过推动数智技术与农业产业的深度融合，不仅开辟集团经济发展新路径，也为履行相关社会责任提供有力支撑。在数智化发展推动下，品品好集团引入数智技术，贯穿研发、生产、管理和市场拓展等关键环节，实现智能化升级，提升产品开发效率和决策支持能力。同时，在社会责任实践中，集团通过平台化履行责任成为企业社会责任实践的新范式赋能相关农业、教育与医疗行业，为有效推进乡村振兴贡献力量。
    本案例旨在启发学员深刻理解企业如何通过数智化技术手段，在追求经济效益的同时积极承担社会责任，实现经济与社会价值的双重增长。通过品品好集团的实践案例，学员可以认识到数智化技术在构建经济价值基础和履行社会责任中的重要作用，从而激发创新思维，助理乡村经济高质量发展。此案例对于企业社会责任、企业管理、创业管理等相关课程的教学具有极高的参考价值，为学员在复杂多变的市场环境中实现可持续发展提供经验借鉴。
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">   Since its establishment in 1996, Qingdao Pinpinhao Grain and Oil Group has closely relied on innovative digital technology to achieve a harmonious coexistence of economic development and social responsibility. By promoting the deep integration of digital technology with the agricultural industry, Pinpinhao Group has not only effectively created new paths for economic development but also provided strong support for fulfilling its social responsibilities. Driven by digital technology, Pinpinhao Group has achieved a comprehensive intelligent upgrade across the entire chain, from research and development innovation, digital production, and precise management to market expansion. This has not only propelled product innovation and enhanced decision-making efficiency but also shaped the group’s responsible brand image. On this basis, Pinpinhao Group further demonstrates its commitment to social responsibility by actively supporting the transformation of related agricultural enterprises, empowering the education and healthcare sectors, and contributing to the effective advancement of rural revitalization.
   This case study aims to inspire learners to understand how enterprises can pursue economic benefits through digital technology while actively assuming social responsibility, thus achieving a dual harvest of social and economic value. By studying the practical case of Pinpinhao Group, learners can gain deep insights into the crucial role of digital technology in building economic value and fulfilling social responsibility, thereby stimulating innovative thinking and promoting social progress. This case holds significant reference value for teaching courses related to corporate social responsibility, business management, and entrepreneurship, providing valuable experience for learners to achieve sustainable development in a complex and ever-changing market environment.
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《数字化与企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SWOT理论；企业社会责任理论；利益相关者理论；数字化赋能理论；企业生命周期理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-02</td>
